social_posts.post_text: First time we’ve ran in full UVU kit down to the socks, this brand has an incredible future ahead - extremely grateful to have the opportunity to steer it with my two best friends. Final drop of the year is 8pm tonight if you haven’t heard. @uvuclub
Weekend work, testing the @nothing Ear (stick) with the team.
Best boy band in the world.  @esquireczech
When that devil on your shoulder is telling you to quit, go faster. @uvuclub
On Friday it felt like 2018 again. @uvuclub

To have two chapters in the @pablotshirtfactory story is incredible, and I am grateful that our paths crossed and we did what we did. Both @cole_buxton & @uvuclub leaving their own mark on Pigalle. Like you said @pabloattal “everything is written, everything is on 🅿️urpose”.

People say they are proud of people or their achievements way too often and it’s lost it’s value, misused and said far too much. But as I sit on this train journey back to London, I can say that I am absolutely proud of you mate, like never before. Thank you, Cole Kenneth Buxton.
